# Energy

Gives a real time current month's usage of Gas and Electricity Services. Also gives an estimate of the next billing cycle's usage.



## Usage [/usage/current/month/{accountNumber}]

### Current Month [GET]
Returns current month's usage information for the provided customer id.

+ Parameters
    + accountNumber: 4859634 (number) - Customer's account number.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        
        {
            "account_number": "4859634",
            "name": "Darko",
            "gas_usage": "20,006 Btu",
            "gas_cost": "짜 46,896",
            "electricity_usage": "3,430 kW",
            "electricity_cost": "짜 12,932",
            "environment": "Japan 1",
            "serviceID": "7777"
        }

## Estimate [/estimate/{accountNumber}]

### Estimate [GET]
Returns an estimate of next month's usage information for the provided customer account number.

+ Parameters
    + accountNumber: 4859634 (number) - Customer's account number.


+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "account_number": "4859634",
            "name": "Darko",
            "gas_estimate_usage": "32,000 Btu",
            "gas_estimate_cost": "짜 46,896",
            "electricity_estimate_usage": "3,430 kW",
            "electricity_estimate_cost": "짜 12,932",
            "environment": "Japan 1",
            "serviceID": "7777"
        }